Package uk.mqchinee.archelia.gui

Class PageableChestMenu

java.lang.Object
uk.mqchinee.archelia.gui.ChestMenu
uk.mqchinee.archelia.gui.PageableChestMenu
public class PageableChestMenu extends ChestMenu
The PageableChestMenu class represents a specialized type of ChestMenu that allows paging through its items. It is an extension of the ChestMenu class, providing additional functionality for managing pageable items.
